Fantastic! Now that you can add and display projects dynamically (via admin), let's build out the About page with a detailed bio, education, and experience sections. We'll also add a functional Contact form using Django's built-in forms and email backend (it'll print to console for now‚Äîeasy to swap for real email later). This uses Crispy Forms (from Step 3) for nice Bootstrap styling.
